'''加巴·拿禾'''（{{lang-en|Garba Lawal}}，{{bd|1974年|5月22日|}}），[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]职业足球运动员，现在[[洛比之星足球俱乐部|洛比星隊]]擔任球員兼助教<ref>[http://www.news.dailytrust.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=4632:lawal-to-join-lobi-as-playercoach&catid=45:sports&Itemid=28 Lawal to join Lobi as player/coach]{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>.。

== 生涯 ==
拿禾在荷蘭球會[[洛達JC|洛達JC]]登上職業生涯的高峰。2009年8月，他重返尼日利亞擔當洛比之星球員兼教練<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en/news/89/africa/2009/09/28/1528863/lobi-stars-garba-lawal-admits-first-match-in-two-years-took-toll- |title=Lobi Stars' Garba Lawal Admits First Match In Two Years Took Toll On Him |accessdate=2010-06-18 |archive-date=2009-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091001204330/http://www.goal.com/en/news/89/africa/2009/09/28/1528863/lobi-stars-garba-lawal-admits-first-match-in-two-years-took-toll- |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他此前曾效力[[布迪治足球會|朱利亞斯貝爾格]]和[[長沙金德|長沙金德]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nationalfootballteams.com/v2/player.php?id=4960 |title=Profile on National-Football-Teams.com |accessdate=2010-06-18 |archive-date=2012-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219190645/http://www.nationalfootballteams.com/v2/player.php?id=4960 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 國際賽生涯 ==
拿禾曾代表國家隊參加了1998年和2002年世界杯。他亦替球隊贏得了1996年奧運會金牌。

== 教練生涯 ==
2009年8 月，他被任命為洛比之星的助理教練<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en/news/89/africa/2009/09/24/1520933/ex-international-garba-lawal-to-make-nigeria-league-comeback |title=Ex-International Garba Lawal To Make Nigeria League Comeback On Sunday |accessdate=2010-06-18 |archive-date=2010-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100123101723/http://www.goal.com/en/news/89/africa/2009/09/24/1520933/ex-international-garba-lawal-to-make-nigeria-league-comeback |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他亦成為尼日利亞U17的球隊協調員<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://worldcup.mtnfootball.com/live/content.php?Item_ID=24511 |title=Garba Lawal To The Rescue |accessdate=2010-06-18 |archive-date=2011-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809111015/http://worldcup.mtnfootball.com/live/content.php?Item_ID=24511 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

